    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Frenzy VR is an action fighter all about destruction &amp; interactive environments. </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can use <strong>any object</strong> as a weapon with our advanced destruction physics for realistic mayhem. Frenzy VR includes a <strong>story mode</strong> with deep narrative secrets, levels, and objectives. Take the chaos into your own hands with <strong>free play modes</strong> allowing unlimited creativity across <strong>various maps</strong> like offices, apartments, prison<strong>,</strong> and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/4440275d4882e7a09972790f764e31c0.avif?t=1763403737\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras_big/4440275d4882e7a09972790f764e31c0.avif?t=1763403737 width=800 height=125 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FULLY INTERACTIVE AND DESTRUCTIBLE WORLDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All maps feature fully destructible items, objects, &amp; enemies</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/e23e38645685692626049d467129dee7.poster.avif?t=1763403737\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/e23e38645685692626049d467129dee7.webm?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/e23e38645685692626049d467129dee7.mp4?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RAGDOLL PHYSICS WITH MELEE / RANGED WEAPONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >NPCs use realistic physics ragdolls for ultimate chaos and mayhem</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/22b546d344837c52db314441e316ccff.poster.avif?t=1763403737\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/22b546d344837c52db314441e316ccff.webm?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/22b546d344837c52db314441e316ccff.mp4?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORY MODE WITH NARRATIVE AND CAMPAIGN</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete the full story with multiple missions and take down the Reborn Company</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/23b8dddf6ad183ffd80df30cb80f0ab9.poster.avif?t=1763403737\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/23b8dddf6ad183ffd80df30cb80f0ab9.webm?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/23b8dddf6ad183ffd80df30cb80f0ab9.mp4?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>10+ REALISTIC MAPS AND MISSIONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Go ballistic in fully interactable worlds built specifically for you to destroy </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/45f14988e69571b2e8e697fde7f07495.poster.avif?t=1763403737\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/45f14988e69571b2e8e697fde7f07495.webm?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/45f14988e69571b2e8e697fde7f07495.mp4?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FULL WEAPON CUSTOMIZATION AND UPGRADES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Realistic gun and melee weapon physics that feel just like real life</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/c3c1fefab5cd171d821aa3c1153ea1b3.poster.avif?t=1763403737\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/c3c1fefab5cd171d821aa3c1153ea1b3.webm?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/c3c1fefab5cd171d821aa3c1153ea1b3.mp4?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FIGHT VICIOUS AND CRAZY NPCS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show no mercy as you fight back against the corrupt NPCs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/16c497d836dd6d52033edaae662f8d33.poster.avif?t=1763403737\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/16c497d836dd6d52033edaae662f8d33.webm?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/16c497d836dd6d52033edaae662f8d33.mp4?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EXTRA MINIGAMES AND GAMEMODES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll never run out of things to do with our our infinitely replayable game modes &amp; Mod Support!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/4beecef66cfab5beb3aa9597bd16dedd.poster.avif?t=1763403737\" width=1170 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/4beecef66cfab5beb3aa9597bd16dedd.webm?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750110/extras/4beecef66cfab5beb3aa9597bd16dedd.mp4?t=1763403737\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
